Summary: Triangular object flying past my south but not observed until after video review.

divs: Sighting Details Earlier today I was participating in a sky watch with Ashtar Command. They were attempting mental contact with extraterrestrials so that they could make their presence known. I entertained the possibility that it might actually work. While on my roof during the event ( 11:30 am to 1:00 pm EST ) I did some panning around hoping to spot something. Only after I looked at my video did I see the white triangle.
